OL,3,CMike Ashley to advise Hornby after
OL,4,Ctaking stake in model train firm
OL,6,FRetail tycoon Mike Ashley is to advise
OL,7,FHornby after building up a stake in
OL,8,Fthe Margate-based historic model train
OL,9,Fbusiness.
OL,11,FThe toy company told shareholders on
OL,12,FWednesday that the Frasers Group
OL,13,Ffounder and majority owner has
OL,14,F"entered into a consultancy
OL,15,Farrangement" with the business.
