OL,3,CMike Ashley to advise Hornby after
OL,4,Ctaking stake in model train firm
OL,6,FShareholders will hope the move can
OL,7,Fhelp spark a financial turnaround at
OL,8,FHornby, after it posted a #5.1 million
OL,9,Fpre-tax loss in the half-year to
OL,10,FSeptember.
OL,12,FShares in the company slipped to their
OL,13,Flowest price for decades at the end of
OL,14,Flast year as a result.
OL,16,FMr Ashley's Frasers Group
OL,17,Fsignificantly increased its stake in
OL,18,FHornby in February this year, driving
OL,19,Fa jump in the firm's share valuation.
