OL,3,CMike Ashley to advise Hornby after
OL,4,Ctaking stake in model train firm
OL,6,FThe Sports Direct owner acquired more
OL,7,Fthan 11 million shares in Hornby to
OL,8,Ftake its stake in the the Margate-
OL,9,Fbased company to 8.9%.
OL,11,FThe move makes Frasers the third
OL,12,Flargest shareholder in the business,
OL,13,Fbehind Phoenix Asset Management and
OL,14,FArtemis Investment Management.
OL,16,FHornby shares rose 7% on Wednesday
OL,17,Fmorning following the update, taking
OL,18,Fits shares to 38p. It gives the
OL,19,Fbusiness a market value of around #64
OL,20,Fmillion.
